Package com.harmonia.constants

Class HarmoniaViewsConstants

java.lang.Object
com.harmonia.constants.HarmoniaViewsConstants
public class HarmoniaViewsConstants extends Object
The HarmoniaViewsConstants class contains constants for the FXML view files used in the Harmonia application. Each constant represents the file path of the corresponding FXML view file. These constants are used to load the appropriate view files in the application. This class should not be instantiated.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Harmonia Team
